'''Nappalatthanar''' ([[Tamil language|Tamil]]: நப்பாலத்தனார்) was a poet of the [[Sangam period]], to whom a sole verse of the Sangam literature has been attributed, in addition to verse 47 of the [[Tiruvalluva Maalai]].<ref name="Vedanayagam_Urai">{{cite book | last = Vedanayagam | first = Rama | author-link = | title = திருவள்ளுவ மாலை மூலமும் எளிய உரை விளக்கமும் [Tiruvalluva Maalai: Moolamum Eliya Urai Vilakkamum] | publisher = Manimekalai Prasuram | series = | volume = | edition = 1 | date = 2017 | location = Chennai | pages = 64–65 | language = Tamil | url = | doi = | id = | isbn = | mr = | zbl = | jfm = }}</ref>
